Gold Advances to Record, Poised to Top $1,600 an Ounce on Demand for Haven

-- B y   P h o e b e   S e d g m a n
-- 
2011-07-17T22:12:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/gold-futures-advance-as-much-as-0-5-in-new-york-extends-gains-to-record.html
Gold futures gained as much as 0.5
percent to a record $1,597.90 an ounce in  New York . The metal
traded at $1,596.80 at 8:11 a.m. in  Melbourne . Gold for
immediate delivery rose as much as 0.3 percent to a record
$1,597.73 an ounce.  To contact the reporter on this story:
